<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Hugo Villeneuve | Aznet</title>
    <link href="/css/tailwind.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/aznet-theme.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      .about-container {
        background: var(--color-900);
        border-radius: var(--radius-double);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 3rem auto 3rem auto;
        padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem 2rem;
      }
      .about-title {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }
      .about-section-title {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      }
      .about-list {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--color-200);
        font-size: 1rem;
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
      }
      .about-list li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }
      .about-contact {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        color: var(--color-400);
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      .about-projects-note {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        color: var(--color-200);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-style: italic;
      }
      .aznet-nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem 0;
      }
      .aznet-nav a {
        color: var(--color-link);
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        padding: 0.3rem 1.2rem;
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        transition: var(--transition);
      }
      .aznet-nav a.active, .aznet-nav a:hover {
        background: var(--color-primary);
        color: var(--color-body-dark);
      }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="shadow-2xl relative z-10" style="background: var(--color-900);">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 flex flex-col items-center">
            <a href="/" style="text-decoration:none;"><span class="aznet-logo">AZNET</span></a>
            <div class="aznet-banner-bar"></div>
            <span class="aznet-subtitle">Your Gaming Tools Hub</span>
        </div>
        <nav class="aznet-nav">
            <a href="/" >Home</a>
            <a href="/about" class="active">About</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="about-container">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-100);">About Me</h1>
                <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--color-300);">
                    Passionate developer creating tools to enhance your gaming experience
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-8">
                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-100);">Who Am I?</h2>
                    <p style="color: var(--color-300);">
                        I'm a dedicated developer with a passion for gaming and creating tools that make gaming experiences better. 
                        My journey started with a simple idea: to solve problems I encountered while playing my favorite games.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-100);">My Mission</h2>
                    <p style="color: var(--color-300);">
                        I believe that gaming should be about having fun, not struggling with tedious tasks. 
                        That's why I create tools that automate the boring stuff, so you can focus on what matters most - enjoying the game.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-100);">My Approach</h2>
                    <p style="color: var(--color-300);">
                        Every tool I create comes from real gaming experience. I play the games myself, 
                        identify pain points, and develop solutions that are both practical and user-friendly.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-100);">Get in Touch</h2>
                    <p style="color: var(--color-300);">
                        Have a suggestion or feedback? I'd love to hear from you! Reach out through the contact form or join our community.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="mt-16 relative z-10" style="background: var(--color-900); border-radius: var(--radius-double); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 2rem auto;">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
            <p class="text-center font-medium" style="color: var(--color-300);">Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Aznet - All rights reserved</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html> 